  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "一个矩阵，其实是一台把平面搬来搬去的机器。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "你喂给它一个向量，它就吐出另一个向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "那么问题来了：这台机器最终把整个平面送到了哪里？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "kernel",
      "line_id": "ker-1",
      "filename": "kernel-ker-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/kernel-ker-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "有些方向很特别，无论向量多长，映射后都变成了零向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "kernel",
      "line_id": "ker-2",
      "filename": "kernel-ker-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/kernel-ker-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "这些被彻底压扁的方向，合起来就叫做核，也就是零空间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "kernel",
      "line_id": "ker-3",
      "filename": "kernel-ker-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/kernel-ker-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "满秩的映射没有核，而降秩时，核就是那条被压没的直线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "image",
      "line_id": "img-1",
      "filename": "image-img-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/image-img-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "再看输出：所有结果向量铺成的集合，就是像，也叫列空间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "image",
      "line_id": "img-2",
      "filename": "image-img-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/image-img-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "满秩时像铺满整个平面，降一秩就塌成一条直线，全零则只剩原点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-1",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/theorem-thm-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "像的维数叫秩，核的维数叫零化度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-2",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/theorem-thm-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "奇妙的是，它俩相加永远等于输入空间的维数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-3",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "在平面里就是：秩加零化度恒等于二，一分不多一分不少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "切换满秩矩阵，看左边的网格被完整搬到右边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "再换成秩一矩阵，红色的核方向瞬间全部坍缩到原点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "核是被映射抹掉的方向，像是映射能触及的天地。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "秩与零化度此消彼长，加起来恰好是维数守恒。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "看懂了核与像，就看懂了线性映射的骨架，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
